taxon.default_photo.attribution: (c) Laurent Qu√©no, all rights reserved, uploaded by Laurent Qu√©no
comments:
[{'jasmin_reh': 'What kind of process did you document here? I would be interested to know! '}, {'edouard-brulhart': 'Hi @jasmin_reh,

This observation has been made for the Digital Botanical Gardens Initiative (https://www.inaturalist.org/projects/digital-botanical-gardens-initiative). This project aims to characterize the chemodiversity of plants in the botanical gardens. The plants are collected and then passed through mass spectrometry to obtain the plants metabolites. For each plant collected we do an iNaturalist entry to obtain the community curation, that permits to highly limitate bad identifications.

If you want to learn more about our project, you can visit this website: https://www.dbgi.org/'}, {'jasmin_reh': 'Thank you for sharing the info. It was very interesting to read. I wish you good luck on the project - sharing knowledge is important for all of us!
'}]
